      "description": "Strength Saving Throw: DC [[lookup @save.dc.value activity=5o0Bh8PQaojx5XMx]], one [[lookup @target.affects.special activity=5o0Bh8PQaojx5XMx]] within 5 feet.\n\nFailure: The target is pulled into the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster}'s space and has the &amp;Reference[Grappled apply=false] condition (escape DC [[lookup @skills.ath.passive]]). Until the grapple ends, the target has the &amp;Reference[Blinded apply=false] and &amp;Reference[Restrained apply=false] conditions, and it takes [[/damage average activity=Exfa4q7O4SvXjGt7]] damage at the start of each of its turns. When the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} moves, the Grappled target moves with it, costing it no extra movement. The [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} can have only one creature Grappled by this action at a time.",
